description.en: FEY is the utility token for all projects associated with WALP Entertainment. On top of that, FEY is an stackable token, where you can earn an annual return from 4.1%-410%. The return depends on the amount which is staked.. WALP Entertainment is the company behind FaucetPay.io. FaucetPay.io was established in 2019 and it is the leading microwallet with over 1 Million users and paid out via faucets over $1.2M in crypto.
